divs: Sighting Detailsone day i was outside, siting on my hammock, when all of the sudden i saw an egg falling from the sky. i didn't know if it was a prank, or if i was getting punked, but i knew that it was none of these things. then suddenly my dogie started barked extra loud, and ran towards it, it did land in the farmhouse. i tried to run after Rex, and when i got there i saw him bleeding on the floor rapidly from the ears, but he wasn't doing anything, just standing there.when the egg shaped thing opened up and i went blind for.....approximately 45 min.... my eye sight finally came back and there were 40 foot prints in the mud, and in my house, the broke the entire first level of the house. there is nothing but soot.
